    "content": "nullSalesforce B2B Commerce and D2C Commerce\nTABLE OF CONTENTS\nClose\nClose\nSearch\nSearch\n Salesforce B2B Commerce and D2C Commerce\n Commerce Basics\n Get Started with Salesforce Commerce\n Import and Export Commerce Data\n Access to Commerce Stores\n Products and Pricing\n Configure Checkout for a Commerce Store\n Store Search\n Search Engine Optimization (SEO) for Commerce\n Commerce Einstein\n Einstein and Data Usage in Commerce Cloud\n Data Cloud for Commerce\n Store Management\n Commerce Promotions\n Considerations for Commerce Promotions\n Configure a Promotion\n Create a Promotion\n Create a Promotion Using a Template\n Create Promotions with Einstein\n Target Customers with a Promotion Segment\n Add a Promotion Tier\n Create a Coupon\n Define a Promotion Discount\n Choose What Qualifies for a Promotion\n Set Conditional Rules for a Promotion\n Localize Promotion Data\n Customize Promotions in Experience Builder\n Promotions in Checkout for B2B (Aura) Stores\n Example Promotions\n Prioritizing Promotions\n Remove a Promotion\n Sell Globally\n Website Design for Commerce Stores\n Publication and Activation\n\nYou are here:\n\nSALESFORCE HELP\nDOCS\nB2B COMMERCE AND D2C COMMERCE\nCreate Promotions with Einstein\n\nUse Einstein and Commerce Cloud data to draft promotions with just a few clicks. Quickly create basic and advanced promotions using natural language instructions and generative AI.\n\nREQUIRED EDITIONS AND USER PERMISSIONS\nAvailable in: Lightning Experience\nAvailable in: Enterprise, Unlimited, and Developer Editions\nAvailable in: B2B Commerce and D2C Commerce\n\n\nUSER PERMISSIONS NEEDED\nTo create promotions with Einstein:\tSmart Commerce Promotions and Recommendations\nIMPORTANT As of Summer ’24, there’s a refreshed Commerce app, which we encourage you to use. The navigation steps in this Help documentation reflect the new app. If you’re still using the previous app, now called the Commerce Storefront Console, see B2B and D2C Commerce Using the Commerce Storefront Console. For instructions on switching to the refreshed app, see Enable the Refreshed Commerce App.\n\nTo use generative AI, first turn on Einstein Generative AI. The EinsteinGPTCommerceAddOn license is also required to create Commerce promotions with Einstein.\n\nIn the navigation sidebar, select a store from the Store dropdown.\nClick Promotions.\nOn the Promotion Preview screen, select a store.\nAdd instructions to the promotion, such as the targeted product, category, or order and the discount or offer.\nTo use one of the provided examples, in the Use Examples section, click +.\nTo use your own instructions, enter natural language text in the box to describe the promotion. To add products or categories, click Search for products or categories and use the search function. To add the product or category to your instruction, click +. After adding your items, click Insert.\nClick Draft Promotion and preview the draft.\nYou can edit the instructions in the box. To update the details, click Draft Promotion.\nTo create the promotion, verify the details, and then click Save.\nVerify that the promotion details are correct on each tab (segments, discounts, qualifiers, and so on).\nWhen you’re ready to activate the promotion, click Active.\nThe promotion isn’t available on your store until you activate it.\nEXAMPLE\n\nWhen creating promotions with Einstein, use natural language. Include specific words and phrases in your instructions.\n\nTroubleshoot and Craft Promotions with Einstein\nWORDS AND PHRASES\tINSTRUCTION EXAMPLE\nTo identify a category or product, use the term “category” or “product” and put the item in single quotes.\tGet 25% off product ‘tennis shoes’.\nFor buy 1 get 1 promotions, use “BOGO” in the instructions.\tBOGO deal: Buy an ‘Alpine Energy Drink’ and get $5 off the second one.\n\nUse the exact adjustment type name in your instructions.\n\nADJUSTMENT TYPE\tINSTRUCTION EXAMPLE\nFixed amount off unit price\tThis is a summer promotion! Get a fixed $25 off unit price on product ‘Tennis Shoes’.\nFixed amount off transaction\tSpecial loyal customer promotion! Get a fixed $50 off the transaction.\nFixed amount off line item total\tEnjoy this tennis essentials promotion. Buy any items in category ‘Tennis Rackets’ and get a fixed $50 off line item total.\nPercentage discount\tEnjoy this summer promotion! Buy a minimum of 2 product ‘Tennis Shoes’ and get 25% off.\nFixed price\tEnjoy this tennis essentials promotion. Buy any product from the category ‘Tennis Balls’ and get it for fixed $3.\nSEE ALSO\nEinstein Generative AI\nEinstein Generative AI & Trust\nEnable Einstein Generative AI\nDID THIS ARTICLE SOLVE YOUR ISSUE?\nLet us know so we can improve!\nYes\nNo\n ",
